### Database Isolation

Every MongoDB document includes `orgId` field:

- Prevents cross-tenant data leakage
- Queries automatically scoped: `{ orgId: session.user.orgId, ... }`
- Compound indexes for performance: `{ orgId: 1, employeeCode: 1 }` (unique)

